title: The Complete Idiot's Guide to the New World Order (2010) pdf
description:
The good, the bad, and the ugly behind the NWO.

The "New World Order" (NWO) is a conspiracy theory; describing the evolution, or existence of one-world government administered by the powerful elite. Now Alan Axelrod offers an understandable look at what the NWO really means to people and lets the reader decide which theories are correct- or whether perhaps it's a little bit of every proposed theory. He discusses:

The Knights of Templar, the Illuminati, the Masons, ancient and modern-day religionists and how they paved the way for a possible Fourth Reich

The link between the lost island of Atlantis, Hitler, and the first President Bush with the concept of a future one-world government

The United Nations, Yale University's Skull and Bones society, the Rockefellers, Morgans, Rothschilds, and Kennedys
